                    <p/>
                </transcript>
                <trailer/>
                <names/>
                <summary>The Mayor of Churchville writes the members of the Staunton bar to warn
                    them that sentiment is growing in the county to pass legislation making it more
                    difficult for lawyers to manage estates.</summary>
                <note/>
                <look/>
            </div>
